OW_CppInstanceProvider Example:

   There are no test units to look at for an OW_InstanceProvider, but our
   internal namespace provider is an OW_InstanceProvider. The namespace
   provider is actually a compiled in provider that is managed by the compiled
   in provider interface. The compiled in provider interface is identical to
   the C++ provider interface. The source code for the namespace provider is:
   
   ./src/server/OW_NameSpaceProvider.hpp
   ./src/server/OW_NameSpaceProvider.cpp
   
   Originally the namespace provider was a C++ provider that was managed by the
   C++ provider interface. We moved it into CIMOM and under the compiled in
   provider interface because it is always required.
   




